-- Conergy Is Close to Sealing Loan Refinancing Accord, Focus-Money Reports
-- Karin Matussek
-- 2010-06-29T05:05:28Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-06-29/conergy-is-close-to-sealing-loan-refinancing-accord-focus-money-reports.html

          
          
             Conergy AG   has almost completed
talks with banks on refinancing 325 million euros ($398.5
million) in loans,  Focus-Money  reported, citing bankers close to
the negotiations.  
 Banks agreed to renew the loans after Conergy posted
operating profit and had a positive cash flow, the magazine
said. A total of 19 lenders are involved in the talks, Focus-
Money said.  
